MonArd
----------
MonArd lets you visually display the CPU and RAM consumption of a server using few LEDs


monard.php
This is the server script. Runs only on *nix

monard_client.php
Requires PHP serial as well as cURL extension. Run as a commandline daemon 


Arduino Sketch
This is the program that controlls the LED bargraph. After the 4th LED, it triggers the buzzer too.